<item>
            <title>[PIG-3430] Add xml format for explaining MapReduce Plan.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3430</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;At Mortar we needed an easy way to store/parse a script&apos;s map reduce plan.  We added an xml output format for the MapReduce plan to make this easier.  We also added a flag to keep track of if each store or load was from the original script (and associated with an alias) or if its a temporary store/load generated by Pig.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
